Bayer Leverkusen defender Emir Spahic could face a lengthy ban after video footage emerged appearing to show him fighting and aiming a headbutt at stewards after a defeat by Bayern Munich on Wednesday night .
Bayeric was substituted in the 90th minute with an ankle injury as Bayer crashed out of the DFB-Pokal at the quarter-final stage .
But amateur footage shows the Bosnian defender involved in an altercation with stewards along the side of the pitch .
Bayer are fourth in the Bundesliga on Saturday .